column1: Dataset name: National accounts, Main aggregates (Eurostat ESA2010 TP, table 1); Frequency: Quarterly; Adjustment indicator: Neither seasonally nor working day adjusted; Counterpart area: World (all entities, including reference area, including IO); Reference sector: Total economy; Counterpart sector: Total economy; Accounting entries: Not applicable; Stocks, Transactions, Other Flows: Labour Productivity (per persons); Instrument and assets classification: Not applicable; Activity classification: Total - All activities; Expenditure (COFOG, COICOP, COPP or COPNI): Not applicable; Unit of measure: Index; Prices: Chain linked volume (rebased); Transformation: Non transformed data
